        "subject": "Mobile App Launch - Eng bandwidth tomorrow morning?",
        "body": "Hey Taylor,\n\nI’m trying to pull together a focused sync on the Mobile App Launch planning before we lock the MOB milestone dates next week.\n\nIdeally I’d like to get Jordan and Sam together for ~45 minutes tomorrow morning to walk through the open planning items on MOB-100 and MOB-101 and make sure we’re aligned on scope before sprint planning.\n\nRoughly sometime between 10:00 and 12:00 ET would be best so it doesn’t collide with the afternoon standups. Do you know if Jordan has any hard conflicts in that window tomorrow? If there’s a better slot in the morning that works for Eng, I can flex.\n\nI won’t send a calendar invite until I hear back from you — just want to make sure I’m not stepping on anything critical.\n\nThanks,\nAlex"
