      {
        "event_id": "planning_v4_email_2",
        "source": "email",
        "timestamp": "2025-11-05T16:56:00-05:00",
        "from": "taylor.brown@company.com",
        "to": [
          "alex.smith@company.com"
        ],
        "cc": [
          "sam.williams@company.com"
        ],
        "subject": "Re: Mobile App Launch - Eng bandwidth tomorrow morning?",
        "body": "Hey Alex,\n\nJordan’s got a deployment window starting just after lunch tomorrow plus a late-afternoon code review, so morning is definitely better.\n\nLooking at our team calendar, Jordan is free between 10:15–11:45 ET. We’ve got a short infra check-in at 10:00, but that should wrap by 10:15. If you target something like 10:30–11:15, that should be safe and still give people a buffer before their midday stuff.\n\nNo objections from my side to you pulling Jordan and Sam into a Mobile App Launch planning sync then. Just include me as optional if you want me there.\n\n-Taylor"
