        "event_id": "planning_v4_slack_dm_1_reply_1",
        "source": "slack",
        "channel": "DM_alex_jordan",
        "timestamp": "2025-11-05T17:35:00-05:00",
        "user": "jordan.johnson@company.com",
        "message": "10:30–11:15 ET tomorrow works for me.\n\nI’ve got a tiny infra follow-up that should wrap by 10:15, but I can hop straight from that into this Mobile App Launch planning sync. I’ll bring updated estimates for the auth and notifications pieces so we can double-check how they line up with the launch timeline.\n\nIf you send an invite, please include Sam and feel free to mark me as required. I’ll be WFH so Zoom is best."
